!! ### Grammar

 +Gram/Comp  !!â‰ˆ * **@CODE@** = Composita !SÃ¦rlig tag til NIQ ajor/saper/artor/nalu- konstruktioner ved transitive verber
 +Gram/Refl  !!â‰ˆ * **@CODE@** = Reflexive, reciprocal or passive !asavoq
